metadata.name: Voyager #1
metadata.description: ToadBoats Voyage is all about the vibrant & colorful ToadBoats; using them to leverage our ability to scale support for young aspiring artists.We believe that the future will be shaped by the artists and creators under our mentorship program. We look to be the go-to resource for tools and support for all new artists looking to thrive in the MetaVerse, as they all learn to say GM. Come support us in their web3 BUIDL journey!
